title: Doctor Who - The Ice Warriors DVDrip H264 AAC
description:
DVD rip of the second doctor story with the two animated episodes. 

The Ice Warriors is the partly missing third serial of the fifth season of the British science fiction television series Doctor Who, which was first broadcast in six weekly parts from 11 November to 16 December 1967. This serial marked the debut of the Ice Warriors. It was the third now-incomplete Doctor Who serial to be released with full-length animated reconstructions of its two missing episodes.
